items.title: Tesla set to open India showrooms in July with made-in-China EVs
items.description: Tesla is set to open its first showroom in Mumbai as early as mid July, which will be followed by one in New Delhi

items.title: Air India reaffirms full co-operation with AAIB, awaits investigation updates: CEO Campbell Wilson
items.description: The airline promised to remain transparent and professional in its communication and urged employees to continue focusing on their roles with care, empathy, and an uncompromising commitment to safety

items.title: Govt restricts import of alloys, chemical compounds containing gold to curb misuse
items.description: The import will be allowed for industrial and manufacturing sectors, including electronics, electrical and specialised chemical industry, against an import authorization, thereby addressing the need of the domestic industry without disruption for actual use, the government said in a statement.
